  "description": "<p><strong>Position:</strong> Cleaner Aunty<br>\n</p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Vacuuming, sweeping, mopping, and taking out the trash</li>\n  <li>Cleaning windows, wiping cabinets, and dusting countertops</li>\n  <li>Helping consultants buy food</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Meticulous</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented</li>\n  <li>Passion</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br>\n3.5 days a week</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Contact:</strong><br>\nIf interested or have a friend to recommend, please contact or WhatsApp us at 8418 5271.</p>",
