    "description": "<p>Where Aesthetics Meets Excellence</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Having successfully served over 10,000 customers in Singapore, Asian Skin Solutions takes pride in being the go-to solution for Asian skin problems. We are committed to help you eliminate your skin concerns in the most relaxing environment, with the most professional, highly-trained therapists. We strive for you to walk out satisfied, pampered, and more confident than before.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Many beauty centres have their services revolve around specific skin problems and issues but we take our research and technology a step further to cater our solutions specifically to Asian skin.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We engage in up-to-date research and new-age skincare technology to customise our solutions to your needs. With our specialised treatments, such as our signature Stemcell Renewal Facial, we work not only on your surface concerns but also on any underlying issues to ensure visible, long-lasting results.</p>",
